      "Section_ID": "SEC_01_DEF",
      "Bullet_ID": "B3",
      "Target_Variable": "BMI_Obese_30_Plus",
      "Statement_Text": "There is a 1.5x higher risk of needing intensive care and having longer hospital stays.",
