      "Section_ID": "SEC_02_ETI",
      "Bullet_ID": "B1",
      "Target_Variable": "Universal_Statement",
      "Statement_Text": "The main cause is bacteria, mostly Streptococcus pneumoniae, though viruses and other germs are also very common.",
