      "Section_ID": "SEC_02_ETI",
      "Bullet_ID": "B1",
      "Target_Variable": "HIV_Positive_on_ART",
      "Statement_Text": "In highly impacted regions, up to 78% of severe cases are linked to underlying immune system weakness.",
